main event: A UFO sighted in Dayton, Ohio on multiple occasions during May 1966.
interesting points: The UFO exhibited a grey color with red and green dots, disappearing below the horizon; The object was described as cylindrical and low in the sky, moving southerly; Witnesses reported hearing a whistling sound coming from the object; On one occasion, the object was tracked on radar; There were multiple reports throughout the month, some concluding the sightings were probable satellites or aircraft.
sighted object: UFO described as having a grey color with red and green dots, cylindrical shape
witness description: A civilian who reported the sighting to the Air Force.
